reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely Beautiful Solar Lights
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the ornesign Ultra Bright Solar Outdoor Light after reading all of the positive reviews and they are even more beautiful in person than originally described on Amazon. They accent the paths around our garden area perfectly and I really like how they shine in a much larger circular surface area. It adds a touch of class when viewing close up or from a distance.These lights have exceeded my expectations and I am going to buy more for my patio and deck behind the house! Simply put, the lighting is warm and quite welcoming!Upon arrival, when I opened the box and started to put the lights together, I was very impressed by how easily each solar unit assembled! And they seem to be very sturdy even though they are lightweight! Being lightweight is a huge advantage as these ornesign solar lights have replaced some older ones I had that were made of very heavy glass and metal. The older ones were heavy and cumbersome. These lights seem to be 100 times better and it was so easy to assemble and place them.About two hours after I placed the lights in the garden path, it began to get dark outside and these lights immediately lit up the area in a beautiful circular projection pattern. I've had them for a few weeks now and there have been no problems. They stay lit for hours and hours at night even after gloomy or rainy days with little sunlight.The price is great and I love how they take one AA battery, so I can easily replace them whenever they run out of juice. This is a really good product that added a nice touch to my home. It exceeded my expectations.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful & easy to assemble/install
reviews.reviewText: These were delivered quickly and packaged very well! They were very easy to assemble and I LOVE the fact that batteries were included. They were charged already so worked immediately/first night. They are not as bright as the photos show, but they do provide enough light to brighten a pathway. The design they put down is also very pretty, but not quite as large as the product photos convey. If the sticks were longer the design would spread to a larger area... but I'm happy with them being about a foot/foot& a half in diameter :) I've only had them installed for 2 days and so far so good!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful solar outdoor light
reviews.reviewText: I bought my first set and they are amazing. Bright but not blinding. The colors are wonderful and the pattern is really cool. Charge great durning the day and last all night.I am surprised with how beautiful these lights look at night. Even with a patio light one, they still shine well. When I posted a picture on Facebook, everyone wanted to know where I got them. They turn my garden and patio into a fairyland! These are really neat. Easy to put together. Charged well on a gloomy day. I love this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Our front yard needed some extra light during these cold snowy months, and these lights have been wonderful! We especially love their radiant design reflected off the snow. The lights were very simple to assemble and they've brought some much needed light during these dark times. It's an added bonus that they rely on solar energy and no batteries are necessary. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic glow and richness to our paved entrance
reviews.reviewText: Love the product elegant and simple to use yet adds richness for a fraction of the cost. Durable as well as self sufficient. Seller was extremely patient with our issue and helped sort it out (broken pieces in transit that was replaced at no added expense). Highly recommended product! Pictures speaks for themselves. Thank you for an amazing product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cool Pattern on Ground!
reviews.reviewText: The lights are working great. I've actually ordered 3 boxes now since I loved them the first time. The pattern that the lights shine is really cool. They are perfect for walkways and other areas of my yard. They seem to glow for many hours into the night.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great lights but one didn't work
reviews.reviewText: I love the light they give off after dark. Very pretty. My only concern is that one of the lights will not light up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love it!
reviews.reviewText: I loved these lights, the light design they form is very cute, I bought two packages, one of each color and I spread them throughout my yard, I loved how they look. I want to buy more soon so they have less space between each other, since my yard is very big lol, I bought them recently and the weather is cloudy and sometimes rainy, but even so, they charge enough with the clarity of the day and they last brilliant all night, imagine the charge they will receive on sunny days and I hope they look brighter than they do now, I also found the price very affordable. I really recommend them!
